    <entry>
        <title>Prompts</title>
        <author>
            <name>Tim</name>
        </author>
        <link href="https://docs.ultimateai.org/prompts/"/>
        <id>https://docs.ultimateai.org/prompts/</id>

        <updated>2025-04-09T12:53:16+10:00</updated>
            <summary>
                <![CDATA[
                    You can save your own PRIVATE prompts to be quickly accessed via "/" during the chat prompt. Note: Although PRIVATE, as always avoid uploading any sensitive or personal information, when using the cloud. You will also see "Global" prompts as saved by myself. How to;&hellip;
                ]]>
            </summary>
        <content type="html">
            <![CDATA[
                <p>You can save your own <strong>PRIVATE</strong> prompts to be quickly accessed via "/" during the chat prompt.<br><em><strong>Note:</strong> Although PRIVATE, as always avoid uploading any sensitive or personal information, when using the cloud.</em></p>
<p>You will also see "Global" prompts as saved by myself.</p>
<p><strong>How to;</strong></p>
<p>Open the "Knowledge Studio" from the Left Panel<figure class="post__image"><img loading="lazy"  src="https://docs.ultimateai.org/media/posts/8/Screenshot-2025-04-09-115022.png" alt="" width="1738" height="229" sizes="(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px" srcset="https://docs.ultimateai.org/media/posts/8/responsive/Screenshot-2025-04-09-115022-xs.png 640w ,https://docs.ultimateai.org/media/posts/8/responsive/Screenshot-2025-04-09-115022-sm.png 768w ,https://docs.ultimateai.org/media/posts/8/responsive/Screenshot-2025-04-09-115022-md.png 1024w ,https://docs.ultimateai.org/media/posts/8/responsive/Screenshot-2025-04-09-115022-lg.png 1366w ,https://docs.ultimateai.org/media/posts/8/responsive/Screenshot-2025-04-09-115022-xl.png 1600w ,https://docs.ultimateai.org/media/posts/8/responsive/Screenshot-2025-04-09-115022-2xl.png 1920w"></figure>
<figure class="post__image">Select Prompts and then click the "+" on the far right to create a prompt<br><img loading="lazy"  src="https://docs.ultimateai.org/media/posts/8/Screenshot-2025-04-09-122402-2.png" alt="" width="1437" height="172" sizes="(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px" srcset="https://docs.ultimateai.org/media/posts/8/responsive/Screenshot-2025-04-09-122402-2-xs.png 640w ,https://docs.ultimateai.org/media/posts/8/responsive/Screenshot-2025-04-09-122402-2-sm.png 768w ,https://docs.ultimateai.org/media/posts/8/responsive/Screenshot-2025-04-09-122402-2-md.png 1024w ,https://docs.ultimateai.org/media/posts/8/responsive/Screenshot-2025-04-09-122402-2-lg.png 1366w ,https://docs.ultimateai.org/media/posts/8/responsive/Screenshot-2025-04-09-122402-2-xl.png 1600w ,https://docs.ultimateai.org/media/posts/8/responsive/Screenshot-2025-04-09-122402-2-2xl.png 1920w"></figure>
<p>Complete the following information;</p>
<ul>
<li>
<p>Title <em>eg: Summarise (unique name)</em></p>
</li>
<li>
<p>Shortcut command  <em>eg: Summary</em></p>
</li>
<li>
<p>Prompt Contents eg: Summarise this text {{CLIPBOARD}}</p>
</li>
</ul>
<p>TIP: Refer later in this page for a list of supported {{VARIABLES}}</p>
<p>You can then invoke the Prompt ShortCut at any-time via "/" and selecting your prompt as shown below;</p>
<figure class="post__image"><img loading="lazy"  src="https://docs.ultimateai.org/media/posts/8/Screenshot-2025-04-09-124503-2.png" alt="" width="1371" height="435" sizes="(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px" srcset="https://docs.ultimateai.org/media/posts/8/responsive/Screenshot-2025-04-09-124503-2-xs.png 640w ,https://docs.ultimateai.org/media/posts/8/responsive/Screenshot-2025-04-09-124503-2-sm.png 768w ,https://docs.ultimateai.org/media/posts/8/responsive/Screenshot-2025-04-09-124503-2-md.png 1024w ,https://docs.ultimateai.org/media/posts/8/responsive/Screenshot-2025-04-09-124503-2-lg.png 1366w ,https://docs.ultimateai.org/media/posts/8/responsive/Screenshot-2025-04-09-124503-2-xl.png 1600w ,https://docs.ultimateai.org/media/posts/8/responsive/Screenshot-2025-04-09-124503-2-2xl.png 1920w"></figure>
<h2 class="mb-xs mt-5 text-base font-[525] first:mt-3"><strong>Advanced</strong></h2>
<p>The below GitHub is an excellent source of information for all things PROMPT related</p>
<ul>
<li><a href="https://github.com/danielrosehill/awesome-llm-prompt-libraries">Awesome Prompt Library</a></li>
</ul>
<h2 class="mb-xs mt-5 text-base font-[525] first:mt-3"><strong>Supported Prompt Variables</strong></h2>
<p>Variables may be used in prompts, the following variables are supported, please ensure to enclose the variable in double curly brackets {{}}</p>
<ol class="marker:text-textOff list-decimal">
<li>
<p class="my-0"><strong>Clipboard Content</strong></p>
<ul class="marker:text-textOff list-disc">
<li>
<p class="my-0"><code>{{CLIPBOARD}}</code>: Automatically inserts the content of the clipboard into the prompt</p>
</li>
</ul>
</li>
<li>
<p class="my-0"><strong>Date and Time</strong></p>
<ul class="marker:text-textOff list-disc">
<li>
<p class="my-0"><code>{{CURRENT_DATE}}</code>: Inserts the current date</p>
</li>
<li>
<p class="my-0"><code>{{CURRENT_DATETIME}}</code>: Inserts the current date and time</p>
</li>
<li>
<p class="my-0"><code>{{CURRENT_TIME}}</code>: Inserts the current time</p>
</li>
<li>
<p class="my-0"><code>{{CURRENT_TIMEZONE}}</code>: Inserts the current timezone</p>
</li>
<li>
<p class="my-0"><code>{{CURRENT_WEEKDAY}}</code>: Inserts the current day of the week (e.g., Monday)</p>
</li>
</ul>
</li>
<li>
<p class="my-0"><strong>User Information</strong></p>
<ul class="marker:text-textOff list-disc">
<li>
<p class="my-0"><code>{{USER_NAME}}</code>: Inserts the name of the user</p>
</li>
<li>
<p class="my-0"><code>{{USER_LANGUAGE}}</code>: Inserts the user's preferred language</p>
</li>
<li>
<p class="my-0"><code>{{USER_LOCATION}}</code>: Inserts the user's location</p>
</li>
</ul>
</li>
</ol>
            ]]>
        </content>
