        <title>Knowledge Collections</title>
        <author>
            <name>Tim</name>
        </author>
        <link href="https://docs.ultimateai.org/knowledge-collections/"/>
        <id>https://docs.ultimateai.org/knowledge-collections/</id>

        <updated>2025-04-09T12:20:26+10:00</updated>
            <summary>
                <![CDATA[
                    You can upload attachments to any chat, however for frequently accessed knowledge you can upload knowledge (attachments\text) for easier assess. Knowledge can then be loaded quickly into any chat via the # command and selecting the knowledge collection. Knowledge can also be added to your&hellip;
                ]]>
            </summary>
        <content type="html">
            <![CDATA[
                <p>You can upload attachments to any chat, however for frequently accessed knowledge you can upload knowledge (attachments\text) for easier assess.</p>
<p>Knowledge can then be loaded quickly into any chat via the # command and selecting the knowledge collection.   Knowledge can also be added to your Own Agents.</p>
<p><strong>How to guide:</strong></p>
<p>Open the Knowledge Studio from the Navigation Bar;</p>
<figure class="post__image"><img loading="lazy"  src="https://docs.ultimateai.org/media/posts/7/Screenshot-2025-04-09-113710.png" alt="" width="1430" height="174" sizes="(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px" srcset="https://docs.ultimateai.org/media/posts/7/responsive/Screenshot-2025-04-09-113710-xs.png 640w ,https://docs.ultimateai.org/media/posts/7/responsive/Screenshot-2025-04-09-113710-sm.png 768w ,https://docs.ultimateai.org/media/posts/7/responsive/Screenshot-2025-04-09-113710-md.png 1024w ,https://docs.ultimateai.org/media/posts/7/responsive/Screenshot-2025-04-09-113710-lg.png 1366w ,https://docs.ultimateai.org/media/posts/7/responsive/Screenshot-2025-04-09-113710-xl.png 1600w ,https://docs.ultimateai.org/media/posts/7/responsive/Screenshot-2025-04-09-113710-2xl.png 1920w"></figure>
<p>Select the Knowledge Tab, then select the + on the far right to create a new collection.<figure class="post__image"><img loading="lazy"  src="https://docs.ultimateai.org/media/posts/7/Screen-Recording-2025-04-09-114722.mp4" alt=""></figure>
<figure class="post__image"><img loading="lazy"  src="https://docs.ultimateai.org/media/posts/7/Screenshot-2025-04-09-115022.png" alt="" width="1738" height="229" sizes="(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px" srcset="https://docs.ultimateai.org/media/posts/7/responsive/Screenshot-2025-04-09-115022-xs.png 640w ,https://docs.ultimateai.org/media/posts/7/responsive/Screenshot-2025-04-09-115022-sm.png 768w ,https://docs.ultimateai.org/media/posts/7/responsive/Screenshot-2025-04-09-115022-md.png 1024w ,https://docs.ultimateai.org/media/posts/7/responsive/Screenshot-2025-04-09-115022-lg.png 1366w ,https://docs.ultimateai.org/media/posts/7/responsive/Screenshot-2025-04-09-115022-xl.png 1600w ,https://docs.ultimateai.org/media/posts/7/responsive/Screenshot-2025-04-09-115022-2xl.png 1920w"></figure>
<figure class="post__image">Complete what you are working on and the purpose (Cosmetic Only), then click "Create Knowledge"<br><img loading="lazy"  src="https://docs.ultimateai.org/media/posts/7/Screenshot-2025-04-09-115217.png" alt="" width="1063" height="568" sizes="(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px" srcset="https://docs.ultimateai.org/media/posts/7/responsive/Screenshot-2025-04-09-115217-xs.png 640w ,https://docs.ultimateai.org/media/posts/7/responsive/Screenshot-2025-04-09-115217-sm.png 768w ,https://docs.ultimateai.org/media/posts/7/responsive/Screenshot-2025-04-09-115217-md.png 1024w ,https://docs.ultimateai.org/media/posts/7/responsive/Screenshot-2025-04-09-115217-lg.png 1366w ,https://docs.ultimateai.org/media/posts/7/responsive/Screenshot-2025-04-09-115217-xl.png 1600w ,https://docs.ultimateai.org/media/posts/7/responsive/Screenshot-2025-04-09-115217-2xl.png 1920w"></figure>
<p>Then click the + on the far right to add documents/directory/text into the collection.</p>
<figure class="post__image"><img loading="lazy"  src="https://docs.ultimateai.org/media/posts/7/Screenshot-2025-04-09-115400.png" alt="" width="1448" height="375" sizes="(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px" srcset="https://docs.ultimateai.org/media/posts/7/responsive/Screenshot-2025-04-09-115400-xs.png 640w ,https://docs.ultimateai.org/media/posts/7/responsive/Screenshot-2025-04-09-115400-sm.png 768w ,https://docs.ultimateai.org/media/posts/7/responsive/Screenshot-2025-04-09-115400-md.png 1024w ,https://docs.ultimateai.org/media/posts/7/responsive/Screenshot-2025-04-09-115400-lg.png 1366w ,https://docs.ultimateai.org/media/posts/7/responsive/Screenshot-2025-04-09-115400-xl.png 1600w ,https://docs.ultimateai.org/media/posts/7/responsive/Screenshot-2025-04-09-115400-2xl.png 1920w"></figure>
<p>Once you see the "File(s) added successfully you  can use your knowledge collection.<figure class="post__image"><img loading="lazy"  src="https://docs.ultimateai.org/media/posts/7/Screenshot-2025-04-09-115514.png" alt="" width="1439" height="243" sizes="(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px" srcset="https://docs.ultimateai.org/media/posts/7/responsive/Screenshot-2025-04-09-115514-xs.png 640w ,https://docs.ultimateai.org/media/posts/7/responsive/Screenshot-2025-04-09-115514-sm.png 768w ,https://docs.ultimateai.org/media/posts/7/responsive/Screenshot-2025-04-09-115514-md.png 1024w ,https://docs.ultimateai.org/media/posts/7/responsive/Screenshot-2025-04-09-115514-lg.png 1366w ,https://docs.ultimateai.org/media/posts/7/responsive/Screenshot-2025-04-09-115514-xl.png 1600w ,https://docs.ultimateai.org/media/posts/7/responsive/Screenshot-2025-04-09-115514-2xl.png 1920w"></figure>
<p>At any time within the chat window press # to select your knowledge with no need to wait for upload delays.</p>
<figure class="post__image"><img loading="lazy"  src="https://docs.ultimateai.org/media/posts/7/Screenshot-2025-04-09-115609.png" alt="" width="945" height="285" sizes="(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px" srcset="https://docs.ultimateai.org/media/posts/7/responsive/Screenshot-2025-04-09-115609-xs.png 640w ,https://docs.ultimateai.org/media/posts/7/responsive/Screenshot-2025-04-09-115609-sm.png 768w ,https://docs.ultimateai.org/media/posts/7/responsive/Screenshot-2025-04-09-115609-md.png 1024w ,https://docs.ultimateai.org/media/posts/7/responsive/Screenshot-2025-04-09-115609-lg.png 1366w ,https://docs.ultimateai.org/media/posts/7/responsive/Screenshot-2025-04-09-115609-xl.png 1600w ,https://docs.ultimateai.org/media/posts/7/responsive/Screenshot-2025-04-09-115609-2xl.png 1920w"></figure>
            ]]>
        </content>
    </entry>
    <entry>
        <title>API Endpoint</title>
        <author>
            <name>Tim</name>
        </author>
        <link href="https://docs.ultimateai.org/api-endpoint/"/>
        <id>https://docs.ultimateai.org/api-endpoint/</id>

        <updated>2025-04-09T11:30:00+10:00</updated>
            <summary>
                <![CDATA[
                    While I recommend our Chat Interface for Maximum compatibility, you also have access to an API Aggregation service that provides all Chat Model via an OpenAI compatible API endpoint. That means that any application that supports OpenAI API and allows setting a custom base URL&hellip;
                ]]>
            </summary>
        <content type="html">
            <![CDATA[
                <p>While I recommend our Chat Interface for Maximum compatibility, you also have access to an API Aggregation service that provides all Chat Model via an OpenAI compatible API endpoint.</p>
<p>That means that any application that supports OpenAI API and allows setting a custom base URL should be supported.</p>
<p>Your API key is available from the "Account" within "Settings".</p>
<figure class="post__image"><img loading="lazy"  src="https://docs.ultimateai.org/media/posts/6/Screenshot-2025-04-09-112335.png" alt="" width="1077" height="715" sizes="(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px" srcset="https://docs.ultimateai.org/media/posts/6/responsive/Screenshot-2025-04-09-112335-xs.png 640w ,https://docs.ultimateai.org/media/posts/6/responsive/Screenshot-2025-04-09-112335-sm.png 768w ,https://docs.ultimateai.org/media/posts/6/responsive/Screenshot-2025-04-09-112335-md.png 1024w ,https://docs.ultimateai.org/media/posts/6/responsive/Screenshot-2025-04-09-112335-lg.png 1366w ,https://docs.ultimateai.org/media/posts/6/responsive/Screenshot-2025-04-09-112335-xl.png 1600w ,https://docs.ultimateai.org/media/posts/6/responsive/Screenshot-2025-04-09-112335-2xl.png 1920w"></figure>
<p>Further documentation is available here;</p>
<p><a href="https://chat.ultimateai.org/apidocs">API Documentation</a></p>
            ]]>
        </content>
